\begin{frame}[fragile]{Using the aesthetic argument more}
We can adjust the way the aesthetics are applied.
\vspace{0cm}
\begin{columns}
\column[t]{0.48\linewidth}
<<aes_gg_4a, fig.width=4, fig.height=3,include=F>>=
